animeTitle: The iDOLM@STER Cinderella Girls: Starlight Stage - 5th Anniversary! "Go Just Go!" PV
animeDescription: An animated commercial by CloverWorks promoting the THE iDOLM@STER: Cinderella Girls - Starlight Stage (iOS/Android game)'s fifth anniversary. The commercial features an animated music video of the song "Go Just Go!" which was released for the game's anniversary.
